et-title widgettitle">FEATURED TODAY</h4> <article class="post-3506789 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-new-features category-gear-reviews tag-hoody tag-jacket tag-micro-puff tag-patagonia tag-synthetic entry"><a href="https://backpackinglight.com/patagonia-micro-puff-hoody-review/" class="alignnone" aria-hidden="true"><img width="700" height="400" src="https://backpackinglight.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Patagonia-Micro-Puff17-700x400.jpg" class="entry-image attachment-post" alt="&lt;span class=&quot;membersonly&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Patagonia Micro Puff Hoody Review" itemprop="image" srcset="https://backpackinglight.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Patagonia-Micro-Puff17-700x400.jpg 700w, https://backpackinglight.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Patagonia-Micro-Puff17-332x190.jpg 332w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></a><header class="entry-header"><h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline"><a href="https://backpackinglight.com/patagonia-micro-puff-hoody-review/"><span class="membersonly"></span> Patagonia Micro Puff Hoody Review</a></h2><p class="entry-meta">by <span class="entry-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span class="entry-author-name" itemprop="name">Max Neale</span></span></p></header><div class="entry-content"><p>Our Patagonia Micro Puff Hoody Review features one of the highest-performing synthetic jackets we&#8217;ve ever evaluated. It&#8217;s performance- and feature-to-weight ratio is extremely high and should be a top pick considered for ultralight backpacking.</p></div></article><h4 class="widget-title widgettitle"><span class="more-posts-title">More New Features...</span></h4><ul class="more-posts"><li><a href="https://backpackinglight.com/nunatak-skaha-apex-review/"><span class="membersonly"></span> Nunatak Skaha Apex Review</a></li><li><a href="https://backpackinglight.com/patagonia-das-parka-review/">Patagonia DAS Parka Review</a></li><li><a href="http